summary: replaces statue of Talos in Whiterun
descriptionHtml:
This replaces the Statue of Talos in Whiterun.
To get the appearances like in the pictures, you should use Flaccid Version of Sundracon Meshes from http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488. 
This mod is based on mannequin. so I suggest you also use Vanilla Mannequin Script Fix v2.1 from http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10652 for this mod.
author: ratoboran
